item.description:
Using in game scene scripts Override _Input(InputEvent @event)
Check if a switch has just been triggered on / off. This mode would use a pinGod game reference to do so.
//pinGod is a reference to the PinGodGame if (pinGod.SwitchOn(&quot;inlane_l&quot;, @event)) { AddPoints(100); } Check a switch state anywhere bool isInlaneOn = pinGod.SwitchOn(&quot;inlane_l&quot;);
